    <pre>

/food/berries?token=[token]    /food/berries/:id?token=[token]
/food/nuts?token=[token]       /food/nuts/:id?token=[token]
/food/fish?token=[token]       /food/fish/:id?token=[token]
/food/oils?token=[token]       /food/oils/:id?token=[token]
/food/greens?token=[token]     /food/greens/:id?token=[token]
/food/seeds?token=[token]      /food/seed/:id?token=[token]
                                       /food?token=[token]
    </pre>


    <h2>Authentication</h2>
    Every endpoint must contain the token to validate your request
    <ul>
        <li>?token=[your token] * don't include the square brackets</li>
    </ul>

